column2: "Darkers approach! Here we are on a new planet! Its name... Wopal!"
"Was that display supposed to accomplish something? Hello, Tea here."
"We finally get a chance to check out a new planet!"
"There's water everywhere, it's like the entire planet is submerged!"
"It definitely seems like an unusual composition. I wonder if it could have been caused by Darkers?"
"Right, Darkers. It could be. But with Dark Falz around, I'd rather not think about that right now."
"There's a state of emergency in effect. If we get called, then I suppose that takes priority."
"It also seems that for some reason, an ARKS distress signal is coming from this planet."
"That's right! I wonder why a distress signal would be coming from a place like this?"
"In a lot of ways, it seems similar to how Naberius was discovered."
"Yeah. Normally, a dispatch order would only be issued to a few ARKS at a time, but this time it went out to everyone."
"Well, we're still investigating, and the native creatures seems pretty violent. Take care!"
